NOTE: The data consists of FACTS about publicly offered scholarships and student aid, gathered
from primary and official sources (state agencies, NSHE institutions, foundations, .gov/.edu
pages). It is not copied from any proprietary aggregator's compiled database. Always verify
details against each record's `provenance.source_url` before relying on them.

